column4: feng: 夥 is only used in the PRC when it means 多.
I know for sure that 硷 is a non-standard (perhaps older) simplification. No longer used. Baidu automatically converts it to 碱.
feng: 馀 is only supposed to be used when necessary to prevent confusion.
feng: 摺 is only used in the PRC when necessary to avoid confusion.
